trans-unit.source: Represents a compound Access Control Entry (ACE).
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Contains flags that specify information about the inheritance, inheritance propagation, and auditing conditions for the new Access Control Entry (ACE).
trans-unit.target: Inneholder flagg som angir informasjon om arvingen arv overføring og overvåking betingelser for den nye tilgang (TILGANGSKONTROLLOPPFØRINGEN).

trans-unit.source: The access mask for the ACE.
The <xref href="System.Security.Principal.SecurityIdentifier"></xref> associated with the new ACE.
Gets the length, in bytes, of the binary representation of the current <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter lengden, i byte for den binære representasjonen av gjeldende <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: This length should be used before marshaling the ACL into a binary array with the <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce.GetBinaryForm*> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne lengden som skal brukes før formidling Tilgangskontrollisten til en binær matrise med den <xref:System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce.GetBinaryForm*>metoden.</xref:System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce.GetBinaryForm*>

trans-unit.source: The length, in bytes, of the binary representation of the current <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Lengden på den binære representasjonen av gjeldende, i byte <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of this <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir hvilken type dette <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Marshals the contents of the <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"></xref> object into the specified byte array beginning at the specified offset.
trans-unit.target: Marshals innholdet i den <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"> </xref> -objektet til den angitt byte matrise med starten fra den angitte forskyvningen.

trans-unit.source: The byte array into which the contents of the <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"></xref> is marshaled.
trans-unit.target: Bytematrise som innholdet i den <xref href="System.Security.AccessControl.CompoundAce"> </xref> er formidles.

trans-unit.source: The offset at which to start marshaling.
trans-unit.target: Forskyvningen der du vil starte formidling.

trans-unit.source: offset is negative or too high to allow the entire to be copied into array.
trans-unit.target: offseter negativ eller for stor til at hele som skal kopieres til array.
